{"tid":697463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院法官將「梁天琦」和強姦犯相提並論","createTime":"2018-06-11T03:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T12:02:15.000Z","uid":134071,"like":37,"dislike":689,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfdf4d9aa41da6895d44fc6fb5c1b4c8bc559c3","tid":697463,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/slowbeat/posts/10155297503437553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fslowbeat%2Fposts%2F10155297503437553&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=569c7618\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/slowbeat/posts/10155297503437553</a><br />\n<br />\nChi Chuen Ray Chan<br />\n24 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n「高院法官今早判刑，指不接受政治訴求為求情理由，亦不容許訴諸暴力，判梁天琦入獄6年。法官彭寶琴舉例指倘若有一強姦犯，恃著事主啞忍再去強姦其他女子，如果法庭知道原來存在第一名沒有作聲的受害人，為何不應考慮這背景。」<br />\n<br />\n一個法官竟然用強姦作比喻，把陪審團未能達成有效裁決的另一控罪比喻作被強姦後啞忍的女子，錯到離晒大譜！"},{"pid":"9efcddca793e4ad9312b19c2556a6fddeb260bbb","tid":697463,"uid":27163,"like":33,"dislike":434,"score":-401,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"有錯？"},{"pid":"83ddbfc6567b6a49f2a541ab024a06ec3a29f6bb","tid":697463,"uid":134071,"like":351,"dislike":16,"score":335,"quote":{"pid":"9efcddca793e4ad9312b19c2556a6fddeb260bbb","tid":697463,"uid":27163,"like":33,"dislike":434,"score":-401,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"有錯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"問得出都顯示你logic有問題...."},{"pid":"0eaa73319e60f8a23a59522aad4bd4efb55ef222","tid":697463,"uid":123335,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"點解我睇唔明"},{"pid":"7912320d3446fc6d6ecdabc75b924b67daf7b1eb","tid":697463,"uid":68598,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:48:05.000Z","msg":"強姦犯姐係確實左佢係已犯罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 