uid":27163,"like":33,"dislike":434,"score":-401,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"有錯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/115856_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F115856_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=902339a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"斷正"},{"pid":"bffc96c0360b562c25e9dc7aa0d431cdb2c3fd62","tid":697463,"uid":153408,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"錯係錯在法庭將未能定罪嘅案件闡述為啞忍的女子。根本就違反在無罪假設"},{"pid":"bf4417cddff27f3b81830abe6bd72cffbbbf6300","tid":697463,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"693a45aa5e6ab85f0a4112d28bdf387d33899035","tid":697463,"uid":160662,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"662ae16c50600c3c3bf12fc6054f2a378af5971a","tid":697463,"uid":174847,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"個官知唔知自己喺度講乜撚嘢？<br />\n <br />\n我就唔明佢講乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"真係唔知佢講乜柒<br />\nBTW 呢個係FB條友講既, 唔知佢有無轉達問題啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"生果報都係咁寫<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303037&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ce726cfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303037&h=b4a32a20\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303037</a><br />\n<br />\n彭官早前在聽取求情陳詞時指，雖然梁面對案發時間較早的控罪未有成立，但他很早便身處現場，自當晚9時開始接連目擊的士事故、警方出動高台等事件，指這些均無爭議，曾問判刑時應否考慮在內，<strong>並舉例指倘若有一強姦犯，恃著事主啞忍再去強姦其他女子，如果法庭知道原來存在第一名沒有作聲的受害人，為何不應考慮這背景</strong>；就本案而言，梁天琦加入亞皆老街暴動前，一直觀察到事態發展，情況有別於一個只出現在亞皆老街的犯案人。"},{"pid":"98cb91525ebb8708441fd0715b80b02775a25989","tid":697463,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"性別歧視 ？<br />\n如果個犯係女人佢會唔會咁講？"},{"pid":"c7d0cb75829465e676de85713cbf742b8d81e03f","tid":697463,"uid":48083,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"0eaa73319e60f8a23a59522aad4bd4efb55ef222","tid":697463,"uid":123335,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"點解我睇唔明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"法官彭寶琴舉例指倘若有一強姦犯，恃著事主啞忍再去強姦其他女子，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果法庭知道原來存在第一名沒有作聲的受害人，為何不應考慮這背景</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n我理解係假定咗佢之前有其他犯罪<br />\n嗰官叫人考慮埋黎判<br />\n<br />\n一來樓主意思係之前既罪行都未入<br />\n<br />\n二來, 我理解法律係一單一單計<br />\n告A考慮A既判刑<br />\n告B考慮B既判刑<br />\n告C考慮C既判刑...<br />\n<br />\n而唔係, 告入C, 就連A, B既判刑都加入埋黎判<br />\n咁咪唔係對等<br />\n而且日後萬一A, B都入咗<br />\n咁咪double count<br />\n<br />\n利申唔識law"},{"pid":"0c4e17d8e015921a38e9cf7d6cd99ee5f2ac5e15","tid":697463,"uid":160662,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bf4417cddff27f3b81830abe6bd72cffbbbf6300","tid":697463,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"693a45aa5e6ab85f0a4112d28bdf387d33899035","tid":697463,"uid":160662,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"662ae16c50600c3c3bf12fc6054f2a378af5971a","tid":697463,"uid":174847,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"個官知唔知自己喺度講乜撚嘢？<br />\n <br />\n我就唔明佢講乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"真係唔知佢講乜柒<br />\nBTW 呢個係FB條友講既, 唔知佢有無轉達問題啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"生果報都係咁寫<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303037&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9