41.000Z","msg":"生果報都係咁寫<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303037&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ce726cfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303037&h=b4a32a20\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303037</a><br />\n<br />\n彭官早前在聽取求情陳詞時指，雖然梁面對案發時間較早的控罪未有成立，但他很早便身處現場，自當晚9時開始接連目擊的士事故、警方出動高台等事件，指這些均無爭議，曾問判刑時應否考慮在內，<strong>並舉例指倘若有一強姦犯，恃著事主啞忍再去強姦其他女子，如果法庭知道原來存在第一名沒有作聲的受害人，為何不應考慮這背景</strong>；就本案而言，梁天琦加入亞皆老街暴動前，一直觀察到事態發展，情況有別於一個只出現在亞皆老街的犯案人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:25:22.000Z","msg":"個官真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩都冇做過都可以係加刑因素，照個狗官既logic 直接判終生都冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d51aa7c36c185f8b124ebc4e66d9f1f35b9421","tid":697463,"uid":117837,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"講強姦案下話??? 我就同你講強姦案<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180124/00176_058.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2F00176_058.html&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fdb8296e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180124/00176_058.html</a><br />\n呢條警犬姦人成孕都係坐五年半咋屌你老母"},{"pid":"91123ec5359c23fe439f8e21613afbfc3896e634","tid":697463,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等佢可以上訴成功無罪釋放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fe9be58d68914fdb6ca928edad42267824a965","tid":697463,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fe73d21240ed6400009fe58f0efb7b8d47dfa2","tid":697463,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9b5c5fc7aca33c532d2f3801625eab26a5d2ead","tid":697463,"uid":141869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab92ad1c2382d39f8e1ad003a8068e1da4efd760","tid":697463,"uid":171177,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"我都明，但問題係個比喻唔貼切，偷換概念，誤導配審團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"判刑仲陪審團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0441372629d604f1a66f48723adf25e6db4316","tid":697463,"uid":96896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，講黎都冇用，香港人都冇得罷免法官，香港不嬲都係法官獨大㗎啦"},{"pid":"e48800575e4b55239607227750581d443c67c5ff","tid":697463,"uid":40033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"姓名：彭寶琴（洋名Anthea）<br />\n<br />\n年齡：56歲<br />\n<br />\n資歷：<br />\n1985年在香港大學取得社會科學學士學位，1993年通過英國曼徹斯特城市大學的法律專業共同試，翌年在港獲認許為大律師。<br />\n1995年加入律政署出任檢察官， 在民事法律科下的民事訴訟組工作；3年後晉升為高級政府律師，被調派至刑事檢控科，其後在基本法、人權、 投訴警察、淫褻物品及賭博組工作，並於2001年考取香港大學法學碩士學位。<br />\n2007年晉升為副首席政府律師，2010年獲委任為區域法院法官，2013年11月15日獲委任為高等法院原訟法庭法官至今。<br />\n<br />\n婚姻狀況：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亡夫歐陽國基生前為水警總區總部（行政）警司，2016年底疑因隱性心臟病突發在鯉景灣住所猝死，彭當時身在外地，由歐陽的水警同袍登門揭發事故。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n曾審理案件：<br />\n東方明珠石油前副主席劉夢熊涉串謀詐騙案；開埠首宗無屍體無法證無招認的謀殺案重審、最終被告陳文琛仍謀殺罪成等。"},{"pid":"e0190edaf1480bb13f540285d56ac695b97a8019","tid":697463,"uid":40033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"以上資料由以下網頁提供<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58206669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58206669&d=UxczTKVknSjmRzO7HfKd9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=242ce162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58206669&h=4e9ac260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58206669</a>"},{"pid":"0cfd23e41a99d7e080da0cd2a6791624af625692","tid":697463,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"判一項控罪要考慮埋<br />\n之前或者之後告的控罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又從法官身上學到野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日笑話: 香港法官"},{"pid":"77e782f41980565d1552291be78e01d157763bc7","tid":697463,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"點解我睇唔到第2個回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}